{"tid":1564535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時用光魔法《榮光》？","createTime":"2019-09-12T22:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T23:05:59.000Z","uid":315038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"290c6dd0906261714d8d70556c3e1633bdde8b49","tid":1564535,"uid":315038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:14:57.000Z","msg":"《榮光》感覺上似用嚟回血回HP，但成用鳩用只會浪費MP/SP，而且正如其他巴打話齋，對敵方冇殺傷力。咁乜時候用最好呢？<br />\n<br />\n我淨係諗閒日，其他有主線任務嘅日子唔諗。我認為喺一個星期嘅中間日子（例如星期三）用嚟回下血比較好，又可以keep住個運動嘅momentum。<br />\n<br />\n另外，回復系魔法通常都可以反傷喪屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，例如嗰啲大台商場show，或者賣港賊嘅喪屍大會。呢啲時候用《榮光》可以扣對手血同埋賺exp<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n咁應該可以避免變嘉年華得嚟又唔會蓋過咗主線任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n(P牌推唔陏)"},{"pid":"74d925d3750397837f74631dc0fe05efc34fc251","tid":1564535,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:15:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"4ff86af358165270b556a60ad8e38814bda3a424","tid":1564535,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"